description: Contains data for time analysis app. Has a near-uninterrupted continuous summary of operations for each well (frac and wireline swaps, frac stages, wireline runs, waiting on offsets), including asset id's for offset wells. This is somewhat time-based as it is updated every 1 minute while a frac or wireline run is ongoing. In addition to that, if a reprocessing of the data is required, this will be updated. I recommend pulling from this collection once the well is complete or performing a full update of records every time pulling.
